You are implementing a Blazor Web App for a university course catalog. The project is already scaffolded at `/tmp/sv-1303458f46da4228ad35a3aa7e11db37/UniversityCourseCatalog/` using Static SSR (`-int None`). 

## Key Constraints (Static SSR)
- No `@rendermode` directives anywhere
- No `@onclick` or event handlers — use form submissions and links
- Forms use HTML POST with `[SupplyParameterFromForm]` and require `<AntiforgeryToken />`
- Query string parameters use `[SupplyParameterFromQuery]`
- No JS interop

## What to implement

### 1. Data Model & Service
Create `Models/` and `Services/` folders in the project root (next to Components/).

**Models/Department.cs:**
